  - specialKeyword: 17
    header: Frozen
    contentText: <color=#FFB430>Unable</color> to take action. The next instance
      of damage taken is increased by <color=#FFB430>50%</color>. <color=#FFB430>Taking</color>
      damage removes this status.
  - specialKeyword: 19
    header: Fortitude
    contentText: Increase the <color=#FFB430>Base</color> Block granted by cards
      by <color=#FFB430>X</color>.
  - specialKeyword: 20
    header: Frozen Mirror
    contentText: When attacked, apply <color=#FFB430>1 Frostbite</color> to the attacker.
  - specialKeyword: 21
    header: Blazing Surge
    contentText: When attacked, apply <color=#FFB430>1 Burning</color> to the attacker.
  - specialKeyword: 22
