    contentText: <color=#FFB430>Cost</color> is equal to your  <color=#FFB430>Max
      Mana</color>.
  - specialKeyword: 24
    header: Steady Barricade
    contentText: "At the start of each turn, retain up to <color=#FFB430>10 \xD7
      X Block</color>."
  - specialKeyword: 25
